    "62207784": {
      "title": "Hybrid dynamical systems",
      "abstract": "Several aspects of model consistency are addressed. The discussion is put in the context of a particular hybrid system, the disk controller. This multilayer hybrid dynamical system is extended to include two other layers: a user layer at the top to define more complex tasks, and a sequencer between the supervisor and the servo layer to permit synchronous control. >"
